      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even talk to people. they just say \"it gets better\" and it's so exhausting hearing that. it doesnt feel like it's gonna get better. it just feels like this heavy, suffocating weight that i cant shake off. i just want it to stop. i just want everything to be quiet.",
