      "content": "it's not a storm. a storm eventually runs out of rain. this is just... nothing. there's nothing left in me. i feel like i'm just dragging this corpse of a life around every day. i don't want a \"path forward\" if the path is just more of this. maybe the only way to actually find actual peace and silence is to just let go of it all.",
